  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/ab40b47dc55c54fe85f59020f9af7003.webp?t=1727621345\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/ab40b47dc55c54fe85f59020f9af7003.poster.avif?t=1727621345\" class=\"bb_img\" width=332 height=64 /></picture></span><br>In this reverse horror game <strong>you</strong> inflict the terror! You've broken out of your containment cell. Now is the perfect time to unleash chaos. It'll take skill to escape alive. There are potential dangers around every corner as you explore what remains of an office. There are signs that someone went here before, a bloody someone.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Eat your enemies</strong> - Office workers may not all be part of this scheme, but is mercy more important than a snack ? Use your sharp teeth to eat almost anything you run into !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/f2850fbc0343594e747be519e808ee9c.poster.avif?t=1727621345\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/f2850fbc0343594e747be519e808ee9c.webm?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/f2850fbc0343594e747be519e808ee9c.mp4?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> <strong>Inflitration & Stealth</strong> - Cut your way through an office filled with guards, cameras and other dangers ! Use stealth to avoid detection of the nearby guards or eat them. Your life depends on it...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/be5225358a391921251496228c70517b.poster.avif?t=1727621345\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/be5225358a391921251496228c70517b.webm?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/be5225358a391921251496228c70517b.mp4?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> <strong>Discover the truth</strong> - Will you uncover the mysteries of your presence in this place ? Find out what happened and who is responsible for capturing you and giving you this fairly well-developed dentition. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/e3cf9222766456e3ded309a5e8c348ff.poster.avif?t=1727621345\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/e3cf9222766456e3ded309a5e8c348ff.webm?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/e3cf9222766456e3ded309a5e8c348ff.mp4?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>  <strong>Avoid the bigger fish</strong> - The unspeakable experiments performed on you made you strong, but you weren't the only test subject. In fact the other may be closer than you think, do not get caught by them or else you will pay the price...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/84652b8adf8e6b9db53845777dbc205e.poster.avif?t=1727621345\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/84652b8adf8e6b9db53845777dbc205e.webm?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/84652b8adf8e6b9db53845777dbc205e.mp4?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><i>Why would you eat a desk ?</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/dcbff83b1ef927d5f1bd77590f114482.poster.avif?t=1727621345\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/dcbff83b1ef927d5f1bd77590f114482.webm?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877350/extras/dcbff83b1ef927d5f1bd77590f114482.mp4?t=1727621345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
